Thirdly, politicall iustice and integritie,Politicall iustice cannot iustifie. when wee are in Mans tribunall and iudgement seat pronounced innocent, and our actions doe answer the prescript rule of humane lawes, cannot yet make vs righteous in the sight of God. Of men-pleasers it is spoken in the sixt of Mathew;
                        Mat. 6.2
